onal operators and next-step operators without nesting; we give a\nnew model construction principle for this one-step logic that relies on a\nset-valued variant of first-order resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 07:16:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
