 MC recommendation methods and benchmark recommendation methods using\nGNNs with tremendous gains, (b) the effectiveness of core components in\nCPA-LGC, and (c) the computational efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 09:27:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Jun 2023 05:33:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 3 Jun 2023 10:02:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2023 15:45:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
