 results constitute a significant step forward in\nthe search of the laboratory observation of a fully-developed weakly-non-linear\ninternal-gravity-wave turbulence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 10:41:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
